http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/Road-development-works-inaugurated/article13989124.ece

Agriculture Minister M. Chandracasu inaugurated road development works at two places in the district at a total outlay of about Rs.22 lakh. A release said that Rs. 7.44 lakh has been sanctioned for developing Narikambai in Nedungadu, Rs.14.56 lakh would be utilised for developing Poovam Yadhaval Road in Kottucherry.Flower show on February 5A three-day flower show will commence here on February 5. Collector E. Vallavan on Friday held a consultative meeting with the officials for evolving arrangements for the show. He said that dance recitals and cultural programmes would form part of the entertainment events at the show.